short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome Extension for Project Ocasta's Webproxy

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically routes your searches through (browse.projectocasta.org)!
This allows you to evade internet blocks and browse your favorite sites!

To use the extension type the word `bypass` into your search bar before the URL you want to visit. You will then be brought to your destination circumventing internet blocks.
